'''Jev Nerran''' was an individual who lived in the [[City/Legends|city]] [[Theed/Legends|Theed]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Naboo/Legends|Naboo]]. Nerran was a neighbor and family friend of [[Jobal Naberrie/Legends|Jobal]] and [[Ruwee Naberrie/Legends|Ruwee Naberrie]] of [[Naberrie family/Legends|House Naberrie]], who lived in the same district in Theed as Nerran. The Naberrie's eldest [[Gender/Legends|daughter]], [[Sola Naberrie/Legends|Sola Naberrie]] and her [[Youngling|children]], [[Ryoo Naberrie/Legends|Ryoo]] and [[Pooja Naberrie/Legends|Pooja Naberrie]], regularly visited Jobal and Ruwee.<ref name="Fact File">{{FactFile|105|NAB 7-8|Sola Naberrie}}</ref> During their trips, they would also visit Nerran,<ref name="Pooja Databank">{{DB|character|poojanaberrie|Naberrie, Pooja}}</ref> spending a great deal of [[Time/Legends|time]] with them and other family friends.<ref name="Fact File" />

==Behind the scenes==
Jev Nerran was first mentioned in the [[StarWars.com]] [[Databank (original)|Databank]] entries for Ryoo and Pooja Naberrie, which were published in [[2002]].<ref name="Pooja Databank" />

